LinkedIn just dropped GAMING. That’s right—the same place where people humblebrag about 20 years of experience in a software that’s only existed for 2 years… now has Sudoku, Wordle clones, and streaks. Because what better way to prove you’re a “thought leader” than by flexing your Mini Sudoku high score on your résumé?

If you’ve ever rolled your eyes at LinkedIn cringe, fake “employee appreciation,” or job postings that make zero sense—this one’s for you.
